p: The study demonstrated that circRAB11FIP1 promoted the invasion of ovarian cancer cells in vitro. Hence, the study identified whether silencing circRAB11FIP1 inhibited metastasis in vivo. The results indicated that silencing circRAB11FIP1 inhibited metastasis in vivo (Fig. S6A and S6B). Also, silencing circRAB11FIP1 inhibited the expression of ATG7 and ATG14 in vivo (Fig. S6C).
